[section#linalg.algs.blas3.rankk
    [:en] Rank-k update of a symmetric or Hermitian matrix
    [:zh_CN] 对称或厄米共轭矩阵的秩-k 更新
]

[para]
[begin:note]
[:en] These functions correspond to the BLAS functions [`xSYRK] and [`xHERK][#:cite@super#blas3].
[:zh_CN] 这些函数对应于 BLAS 函数 [`xSYRK] 和 [`xHERK][#:cite@super#blas3]。
[end:note]

[para]
[:en] The following elements apply to all functions in [#linalg.algs.blas3.rankk].
[:zh_CN] 下列要素适用于 [#linalg.algs.blas3.rankk] 中的所有函数。

[para]
[:en] For any function [`F] in this subclause with a parameter named [`t],
an [`InMat2] template parameter, and a function parameter [`InMat2 E],
[`t] applies to accesses done through the parameter [`E].
[:zh_CN] 对于本子条款中任何带有名为 [`t] 的形参，模板形参 [`InMat2]，以及函数形参
[`InMat2 E] 的函数 [`F]，[`t] 适用于通过形参 [`E] 所进行的访问。

[:en] [`F] only accesses the triangle of [`E] specified by [`t].
[:zh_CN] [`F] 仅访问 [`t] 所指定的 [`E] 的三角部分。

[:en] For accesses of diagonal elements [`E`[i, i`]], [`F] only uses the value
[`[*real-if-needed](E`[i, i`])] if the name of [`F] starts with [`hermitian].
[:zh_CN] 对于对角线元素 [`E`[i, i`]] 的访问，如果 [`F] 的名字以 [`hermitian] 开始，
则仅使用值 [`[*real-if-needed](E`[i, i`])]。

[:en] For accesses [`E`[i, j`]] outside the triangle specified by [`t], [`F] only uses the value
[:zh_CN] 对于 [`t] 所指定三角部分之外的访问 [`E`[i, j`]]，[`F] 仅使用以下值：
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`[*conj-if-needed](E`[j, i`])] if the name of [`F] starts with [`hermitian], or
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`F] 的名字以 [`hermitian] 开始，则使用 [`[*conj-if-needed](E`[j, i`])]，或者
[item]
[:en] [`E`[j, i`]] if the name of [`F] starts with [`symmetric].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`F] 的名字以 [`symmetric] 开始，则使用 [`E`[j, i`]]。
[list:end]

[para:mandates]
[list]
[item]
[:en] If [`OutMat] has [`layout_blas_packed] layout, then the layout[=']s [`Triangle]
template argument has the same type as the function[=']s [`Triangle] template argument;
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`OutMat] 具有 [`layout_blas_packed] 布局，则该布局的 [`Triangle]
模板实参与函数的 [`Triangle] 模板实参为相同类型；
[item]
[:en] If the function has an [`InMat2] template parameter and if [`InMat2] has
[`layout_blas_packed] layout, then the layout[=']s [`Triangle] template argument
has the same type as the function[=']s [`Triangle] template argument;
[:zh_CN] 如果函数带有模板形参 [`InMat2] 且 [`InMat2] 具有 [`layout_blas_packed]
布局，则该布局的 [`Triangle] 模板实参与函数的 [`Triangle] 模板实参为相同类型；
[item]
[:en] [`[*possibly-multipliable]<decltype(A), decltype(transposed(A)), decltype(C)>()] is [`true]; and
[:zh_CN] [`[*possibly-multipliable]<decltype(A), decltype(transposed(A)), decltype(C)>()] 为 [`true]；并且
[item]
[:en] [`[*possibly-addable]<decltype(C), decltype(E), decltype(C)>()] is [`true]
for those overloads with an [`E] parameter.
[:zh_CN] 对于带有形参 [`E] 的重载，[`[*possibly-addable]<decltype(C), decltype(E), decltype(C)>()] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:expects]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`[*multipliable](A, transposed(A), C)] is [`true]; and
[:zh_CN] [`[*multipliable](A, transposed(A), C)] 为 [`true]；并且
[begin:note]
[:en] This implies that [`C] is square.
[:zh_CN] 这意味着 [`C] 是方阵。
[end:note]
[item]
[:en] [`[*addable](C, E, C)] is [`true] for those overloads with an [`E] parameter.
[:zh_CN] 对于带有形参 [`E] 的重载，[`[*addable](C, E, C)] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:complexity]
[:en] [?bigoh [`A.extent(0)] \times [`A.extent(1)] \times [`A.extent(0)]].
[:zh_CN] [?bigoh [`A.extent(0)] \times [`A.extent(1)] \times [`A.extent(0)]]。

[para:remarks]
[:en] [`C] may alias [`E] for those overloads with an [`E] parameter.
[:zh_CN] 对于带有形参 [`E] 的重载，[`C] 可能为 [`E] 的别名。
[div:end]

[%@lib symmetric_matrix_rank_k_update]
[codeblock:declaration]
  template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]scalar Scalar, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat, [[redoc("*:c>")]]possibly-packed-out-matrix OutMat, class Triangle>
    void symmetric_matrix_rank_k_update(Scalar alpha, InMat A, OutMat C, Triangle t);
  template<class ExecutionPolicy, [[redoc("*:c>")]]scalar Scalar,
           [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat, [[redoc("*:c>")]]possibly-packed-out-matrix OutMat, class Triangle>
    void symmetric_matrix_rank_k_update(ExecutionPolicy&& exec,
                                        Scalar alpha, InMat A, OutMat C, Triangle t);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Computes [$C = \alpha A A^T], where the scalar [$\alpha] is [`alpha].
[:zh_CN] 计算 [$C = \alpha A A^T]，其中标量 [$\alpha] 为 [`alpha]。
[div:end]

[%@lib hermitian_matrix_rank_k_update]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]scalar Scalar, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat, [[redoc("*:c>")]]possibly-packed-out-matrix OutMat,
         class Triangle>
  void hermitian_matrix_rank_k_update(Scalar alpha, InMat A, OutMat C, Triangle t);
template<class ExecutionPolicy, [[redoc("*:c>")]]scalar Scalar, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat,
         [[redoc("*:c>")]]possibly-packed-out-matrix OutMat, class Triangle>
  void hermitian_matrix_rank_k_update(ExecutionPolicy&& exec, Scalar alpha, InMat A,
                                      OutMat C, Triangle t);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Computes [$C = \alpha A A^H], where the scalar [$\alpha] is [`[*real-if-needed](alpha)].
[:zh_CN] 计算 [$C = \alpha A A^H]，其中标量 [$\alpha] 为 [`[*real-if-needed](alpha)]。
[div:end]

[%@lib symmetric_matrix_rank_k_update]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]scalar Scalar, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]possibly-packed-out-matrix OutMat,
         class Triangle>
void symmetric_matrix_rank_k_update(Scalar alpha, InMat1 A, InMat2 E, OutMat C, Triangle t);
template<class ExecutionPolicy, [[redoc("*:c>")]]scalar Scalar, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat2,
         [[redoc("*:c>")]]possibly-packed-out-matrix OutMat, class Triangle>
void symmetric_matrix_rank_k_update(ExecutionPolicy&& exec, Scalar alpha, InMat1 A, InMat2 E,
                                    OutMat C, Triangle t);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Computes [$C = E + \alpha A A^T], where the scalar [$\alpha] is [`alpha].
[:zh_CN] 计算 [$C = E + \alpha A A^T]，其中标量 [$\alpha] 为 [`alpha]。
[div:end]

[%@lib hermitian_matrix_rank_k_update]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]scalar Scalar, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat2, [[redoc("*:c>")]]possibly-packed-out-matrix OutMat,
         class Triangle>
void hermitian_matrix_rank_k_update(Scalar alpha, InMat1 A, InMat2 E, OutMat C, Triangle t);
template<class ExecutionPolicy, [[redoc("*:c>")]]scalar Scalar, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat1, [[redoc("*:c>")]]in-matrix InMat2,
         [[redoc("*:c>")]]possibly-packed-out-matrix OutMat, class Triangle>
void hermitian_matrix_rank_k_update(ExecutionPolicy&& exec, Scalar alpha, InMat1 A, InMat2 E,
                                    OutMat C, Triangle t);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Computes [$C = E + \alpha A A^H], where the scalar [$\alpha] is [`[*real-if-needed](alpha)].
[:zh_CN] 计算 [$C = E + \alpha A A^H]，其中标量 [$\alpha] 为 [`[*real-if-needed](alpha)]。
[div:end]
